      <h3>මෑතකාලීන ඉදිරි දර්ශන</h3>
      <ul>
        
          
            <li><a href="/en/articles/2020/07/06/pers-j06.html#pk_campaign=sidebar&pk_kwd=perspectives">The significance of the July 4 online discussion, “The Place of the Two American Revolutions: Past, Present and Future” (06/07/2020)</a></li>
          
        
          
            <li><a href="/en/articles/2020/07/04/pers-j04.html#pk_campaign=sidebar&pk_kwd=perspectives">The two American Revolutions in world history (04/07/2020)</a></li>
          
        
          
